<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.8.2">
<l>tuvarā ṭaiyuṭut toruceṇ ṭuciluppi</l>
<l>kavarā kamuṭit tu<supplied>k</supplied>kalik kaccu<supplied>k</supplied>kaṭṭi</l>
<l>cuvarār kataviṉ puṟamē vantuniṉṟīr</l>
<l>ivarā rituveṉ ṉituveṉ ṉituveṉṉō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You came and stood outside the door of the wall,</l>
<l>Wearing red raiments, tightly binding a belt,</l>
<l>Tying [your hair] in two, twirling a ball.</l>
<l>Who is he? What is this? What is this? What is this?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
